<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sitemap - Jyotsna's NCBI Tools</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Site navigation map for Jyotsna's NCBI Tools, offering biotech and genomic sequence analysis tools for researchers.">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .sitemap-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .sitemap-section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .sitemap-section h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .sitemap-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .sitemap-list li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .sitemap-list a {
            display: block;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
        }
        
        .sitemap-list a:hover {
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }
        
        .sitemap-list a i {
            margin-right: 8px;
            color: #3498db;
        }
        
        .sitemap-description {
            font-size: 0.85em;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 5px;
            margin-left: 27px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="header-content">
                <h1>Sitemap</h1>
                <p class="header-subtitle">Navigation Guide to Jyotsna's NCBI Tools</p>
                <a href="/" class="back-link"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Home</a>
            </div>
        </header>
        
        <div class="sitemap-container">
            <div class="sitemap-section">
                <h2>Main Pages</h2>
                <ul class="sitemap-list">
                    <li>
                        <a href="/"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Home</a>
                        <p class="sitemap-description">Main page with access to all bioinformatics and sequence analysis tools</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="sitemap-section">
                <h2>Analysis Tools</h2>
                <ul class="sitemap-list">
                    <li>
                        <a href="/sequence-comparison"><i class="fas fa-dna"></i> Sequence Comparison Tool</a>
                        <p class="sitemap-description">Compare DNA/RNA sequences to identify mutations and generate analysis reports</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/dna-analysis"><i class="fas fa-microscope"></i> DNA Sequence Analysis</a>
                        <p class="sitemap-description">Analyze nucleotide composition of DNA sequences from NCBI</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/blast-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-search"></i> BLAST Sequence Search</a>
                        <p class="sitemap-description">Search nucleotide and protein databases using NCBI BLAST</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/nucleotide-download"><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Nucleotide Sequence Downloads</a>
                        <p class="sitemap-description">Download and export nucleotide sequences from NCBI</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/sequence-fetch"><i class="fas fa-file-download"></i> Sequence Fetch Tool</a>
                        <p class="sitemap-description">Fetch and analyze nucleotide sequences from NCBI database</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/variant-analysis"><i class="fas fa-project-diagram"></i> Variant Analysis Tool</a>
                        <p class="sitemap-description">Analyze genetic variants using Ensembl REST API</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/design-primers"><i class="fas fa-edit"></i> SNP Primer Designer</a>
                        <p class="sitemap-description">Design PCR primers for SNP genotyping with optimized parameters</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/sequence-indexer"><i class="fas fa-sort-numeric-up"></i> Sequence Character Indexer</a>
                        <p class="sitemap-description">Index and analyze character distribution in sequences</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="sitemap-section">
                <h2>Additional Resources</h2>
                <ul class="sitemap-list">
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://github.com/priyamjyotsna" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-github"></i> GitHub Repository</a>
                        <p class="sitemap-description">Source code and development information</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://orcid.org/0000-0001-8782-9783" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-orcid"></i> ORCID Profile</a>
                        <p class="sitemap-description">Research and publication information</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 